Summary: I saw three bright orange orbs in a row, moving slowly across the sky. I tried to follow them and I took a picture with my phone. Then they disappeared, like they went straight up. When I went back to my seat, I looked up and two more came along.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting outside at a restaurant in Highwood Illinois last night. I looked up and saw three bright orange orbs moving in a line across the sky. I got up to follow them and take a picture. They disappeared. I sat back down at the table and looked up. Two more came along the same path.
